</p><p class="css-1hno3qs e190yofl0">至少有 1,200 个专门的马术俱乐部。在旁遮普邦的田野里，在拉达克危险的山坡上，可以看到覆盖着锈迹斑斑的标本，在城市街道上躲避牛和汽车。对于宝莱坞英雄和恶棍来说，它都是不可或缺的装备。印度武装部队于 1949 年订购了 500 辆两轮车用于该国北部边境巡逻，首次引发了印度“子弹”热潮，该部队拥有一支专门驾驶“子弹”的特技团队。 2017 年，龙卷风队（该队的名字）完成了用一辆摩托车载运 58 人的壮举。</p><p class="css-1hno3qs e190yofl0">所有这些，再加上这些机器似乎永远不会过期，并且几乎任何人都可以在任何地方修理，这解释了 Bullet 经久不衰的受欢迎程度。对于许多难以想象拥有一套房子甚至一辆汽车的印度人来说，Bullet 不仅令人向往，而且每辆 2,400 美元的价格几乎是可以买到的。既然吸引力如此不变，谁还需要改变呢？ <span class="ufinish">■</span></p><p class="css-1hno3qs e190yofl0"><i>要掌握商业和技术领域最重大的新闻，请订阅我们的每周订阅者<a href="https://www.economist.com/newsletters/the-bottom-line">简讯“底线”</a> 。</i></p></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 07 Sep 2023 14:20:20 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> /内容/6flkt73o13b0pbqru5rhdohfochaikaf</guid><link/> https://www.economist.com/business/2023/09/07/meet-the-worlds-most-enduring-product </item><item><title><![CDATA[Networking for introverts: a how-to guide]]></title><description><![CDATA[<section class="css-1ugvd2u e18wk22u0"><style data-emotion="css qts40t">.css-qts40t img{display:block;}.css-qts40t .edweubf2{margin-top:0.25rem;}</style><figure class="css-qts40t e1197rjj0"><img alt="" fetchpriority="high" width="1280" height="720" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 960px) 700px, 95vw" srcset="https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=360,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230909_WBD002.jpg 360w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=384,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230909_WBD002.jpg 384w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=480,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230909_WBD002.jpg 480w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=600,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230909_WBD002.jpg 600w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=834,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230909_WBD002.jpg 834w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=960,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/2